15/3/25 - v1.0
  Update for QT6

15/3/25  - v0.2
  Refactoring and additions
    Ability to manually merge colours
    Brightness, contrast and saturation adjustment

28/5/21  - v0.1
  First version with basic features:
     GUI which can load images, resize and recolour
     Recolour to fixed colour chart, with closest-match picker
     Ability to save image
     Ability to save a pattern with title, key, length and size estimates etc
     More complex features unimplemented - no change tracking, undo, better image manipulation
